MAP.COMMENT: Query for extraction of TN certs

Values.value: select distinct p.CORPORATIONNAME, p.STATUS, c.EXPIRATIONDATE from PARTNER p, CERTIFICATEDATA c where p.PARTNERID=c.ownerid and p.STATUS='Active' order by p.CORPORATIONNAME asc
